@startuml

STATE_MACHINE DigitalWatch

[*] InitialState --> ViewTime
ViewTime --> AdjustTime
AdjustTime --> HourMode [user submits]
HourMode --> IncreaseHour
IncreaseHour --> AdjustTime
AdjustTime --> MinuteMode [user submits]
MinuteMode --> IncreaseMinute
IncreaseMinute --> AdjustTime
AdjustTime --> AlarmMode [user submits]
AlarmMode --> AlarmOnOff [user submits]
AlarmOnOff --> AlarmOn
AlarmOn --> SetAlarmTime [user submits]
SetAlarmTime --> CheckAlarmTime [system validates]
CheckAlarmTime --> MatchCurrentTime [current time matches set alarm time]
MatchCurrentTime --> TriggerAlarm
TriggerAlarm --> Ringing
Ringing --> AlarmOff [user presses specific button]
AlarmOff --> InitialState
AlarmOnOff --> AlarmOff
InitialState --> LightMode [user submits]
LightMode --> LightOn
LightOn --> LightOff [button released]
LightOff --> InitialState

@enduml
